  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20081119234725/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/4/" target="_top">匿名</a><a href="/web/20081119234725/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#medal" target="_top"><img src="/web/20081119234725im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/star_gold.png" border=0/></a><a href="/web/20081119234725/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20081119234725im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
